---
title: Lemony Summer Wild Rice  with Roasted Grapes and Broccolini
description: Savoury wild rice mingles with the sweetness of roasted grapes, as the perfect complement to tender broccolini and crunchy almonds in this vibrant vegetarian dish. Each bite is a harmonious symphony of flavours and textures!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1046_W29_CA_RV26213-1_Main_low-efb3b7a2.jpg
